{{Doomwiki}}
QZDoom is a source port based on [[GZDoom]] coded and maintained by [[User:Eruanna|Eruanna]] and dpJudas. It was created as a fork of [[GZDoom]] to develop experimental rendering features, and includes truecolor rendering in software as well as a polygonal software renderer. It's hoped that most features that require OpenGL rendering might be supported in software rendering in QZDoom. The most recent stable version of QZDoom is {{LatestQZDoom}}.

